cf92d1a88712352db0613bd1afaebaa48","tid":1458232,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:49:20.000Z","msg":"第245章 《公安條例》 第40條 行政長官授權他人委任特務警察的權力<br />\n版本:<br />\n(版本於 19970630)<br />\n(版本於 19970701)<br />\n(版本於 20170215)*<br />\n<br />\n對照任何兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n行政長官可隨時藉命令授權警務處處長，以書面方式委任任何願意擔任特務警察的人為特務警察，任期由行政長官在該命令中指明。<br />\n(由1970年第31號第25條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)"},{"pid":"9a7ad4702c619fd1d3d010789b61ed122cbc7da7","tid":1458232,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"第245章 《公安條例》 第41條 特務警察的權力<br />\n版本:<br />\n(版本於 19970630)<br />\n(版本於 20170215)*<br />\n<br />\n對照任何兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n(1)獲委為特務警察的人，在以該身分行事時所具備的職責、權力、保障及豁免權，均與本條例或任何其他法律所委予或授予警務人員的職責、權力、保障及豁免權相同。<br />\n(2)特務警察須遵從警務處處長向其作出的所有命令。<br />\n(3)本條的規定並不使特務警察有權獲得任何薪酬、退休金或其他報酬。"},{"pid":"f8e7de3c3e90fcf89de72ff5fd6cf72383529b09","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a7ad4702c619fd1d3d010789b61ed122cbc7da7","tid":1458232,"uid":57397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"第245章 《公安條例》 第41條 特務警察的權力<br />\n版本:<br />\n(版本於 19970630)<br />\n(版本於 20170215)*<br />\n<br />\n對照任何兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n(1)獲委為特務警察的人，在以該身分行事時所具備的職責、權力、保障及豁免權，均與本條例或任何其他法律所委予或授予警務人員的職責、權力、保障及豁免權相同。<br />\n(2)特務警察須遵從警務處處長向其作出的所有命令。<br />\n(3)本條的規定並不使特務警察有權獲得任何薪酬、退休金或其他報酬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:52:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要問係咪永久居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722967dfacc71d185e5b5fa748632a065d82e39b","tid":1458232,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4016ce3100d50d99f5cab8b9a14f45d30a6fec1","tid":1458232,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"下次要問嗰啲警察係吙尸香港永久性居民"},{"pid":"f12fbb24607f0187ac8764052b00ee0471330af0","tid":1458232,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1335cfe7840d9dc50c4ac1eac7be90c27e7a83","tid":1458232,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:57:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de2a7458d0ad5eed6fac9faabe236bf8c9c847e2","tid":1458232,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:58:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62875817473636e2c2ae6fe8a042e701d2374078","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:58:38.000Z","msg":"永久居民呀"},{"pid":"c4c8fd8e1f4241f4c04c31e0bc8d2db0a25fa41b","tid":1458232,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:59:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2da05d90bee3a59ddc9da80a2b004c097b6ab5a0","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:04:34.000Z","msg":"永久居民!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"d08878d6903952207eb7a4fcca23d7afa329c969","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:04:56.000Z","msg":"永久居民!!!!"},{"pid":"0a53b2cbe3bef8a2e1781841733358202d7f9995","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:23:34.000Z","msg":"人手推, 起碼上一次熱門先啦屌"},{"pid":"6e1206c5457e46e90d187782d23e52daaccc5fe6","tid":1458232,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"唔好講推 將今日核彈列明黎推post<br />\n<br />\n1. 射頭<br />\n2. 721無起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者<br />\n4. 無啦啦拘捕個女人<br />\n5. 室內開槍<br />\n6. 過份使用武力+催淚彈<br />\n7. 冇委任證<br />\n8. 過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警黑勾結<br />\n10. 無差別濫捕<br />\n11. 光明正大講大話<br />\n12. 誣蔑市民+陷害市民<br />\n13. 拆證物<br />\n14. 無視任何法律及指引<br />\n<br />\n佢地搞到香港咁樣 人人都生意差冇工開佢地仲計ot幾萬蚊準時出糧一定唔驚，諗計斷班撚樣既飯碗<br />\n香港人唔再需要唔保護市民既警察！！唔想再出糧俾一啲開槍打我 用棍扑我既人"},{"pid":"95da13327500c04c94cf2b42eaa94703d81d6716","tid":1458232,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T01:49:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0278f16e88b389006167b7f53c35b71667a275ad","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"推下得唔得"},{"pid":"830bc7d82da8500577953dc2ae57d1237e918251","tid":1458232,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"唔通佢否認咗就可信咩？大家知咩事啦"},{"pid":"50ea3d68c1348293a5d063e70a73535823272ad2","tid":1458232,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ee1360ba5db5e8fa83bebaf4c223221303765f3","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"今日記者會佢只係講所有警察都係根據公務員事務局同香港警務處正式取錄, 無正面回應入面有無武警公安<br />\n如果好似之前有巴打引用香港警務處可以隨時委任有需要既人執行任務, 佢呢個講法係好 tricky<br />\n可以用左公安同武警, 但係從警務處正式委任<br />\n<br />\n下次記者應該問呢2個月既防暴入面有無唔係香港永久居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:50:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f9201f3c860e8e7278bafebf92d08a0e8e2e8594","tid":1458232,"uid":33125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:06:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a09bb3d21ee458ece22f2f4a7f54ab26